question: 脚
sourceAnswer: foot/paw/arm-(of-an-octopus,-squid,-etc.) | leg | gait | pace | bottom-structural-component-(i.e.-radical)-of-a-kanji | means-of-transportation | money/coin
sourceMnemonic: The kanji and the word are exactly the same. That means they share meanings as well.
